---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — CA Accounting | AICPA-Member Firm in Glendale, CA"
  description="An AICPA-member accounting firm headquartered in Glendale, California. Founded by Farshid Khosravi, EA, and led with Managing Partner Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">About</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          A Los Angeles firm headquartered in Glendale.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          CA Accounting is a local Glendale, CA accounting firm providing local businesses and individuals with tax and accounting services. We work to reduce expenses, increase productivity, and translate knowledge into savings for our clients.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Story -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">How we work.</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We will be your partners in getting your books on point. That process involves analyzing trends and patterns in your numbers, and developing financial solutions to meet your overall goals and objectives.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            For business owners, we work to reduce your expenses and increase your productivity. For individuals, we focus on tax strategies that maximize income and minimize taxes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed">
            Every new engagement starts with a free initial consultation, so we can understand your situation before recommending an approach.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">Our standards.</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
            CA Accounting is a member firm of the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants (AICPA).
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed">
            The firm is led by a Certified Public Accountant and an Enrolled Agent.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Leadership</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          The partners.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <div class="aspect-square w-48 mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-navy-deep">
            <img src="/images/team/farshid.jpg" alt="Farshid Khosravi, EA" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-1">Farshid Khosravi, EA</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/60 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Founding Partner</p>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Farshid is the founding partner of CA Accounting and an Enrolled Agent, a federal credential issued by the U.S. Department of the Treasury authorizing him to represent taxpayers before the Internal Revenue Service.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="aspect-square w-48 mb-6 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-navy-deep">
            <img src="/images/team/narek.jpg" alt="Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-1">Narek Mkhitaryan, CPA</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/60 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Managing Partner</p>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Narek is the managing partner of CA Accounting and a Certified Public Accountant.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values / Principles -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12 fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">What We Stand For</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy">
          Principles that show up in the work.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Tax minimization, year-round</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Annual tax return preparation paired with year-round tax minimization planning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-navy mb-3">Confidentiality</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            CA Accounting is bound by professional standards and ethics. We strive to ensure that your information is always protected and your right to privacy is honored and respected.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Client voice -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-cream-warm">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in">
          <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-6xl leading-none mb-2 select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
          <blockquote class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-serif">
            His counsel is invaluable. What I value most about Farshid is his unimpeachable integrity.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="border-t border-line pt-4">
            <p class="text-navy font-semibold text-sm">Joe Cangelosi</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Client</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-6xl leading-none mb-2 select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
          <blockquote class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-serif">
            Trust is pre-eminent in any lasting and fulfilling relationship... you've forged this bond of trust.
          </blockquote>
          <div class="border-t border-line pt-4">
            <p class="text-navy font-semibold text-sm">Jay Miller</p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Client</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 fade-in">
        <a href="/testimonials" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Read all client stories →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Ready to talk?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free initial consultation. We will listen to where your business is and tell you how we can help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn-modern bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="/team"
            class="btn-modern border border-navy text-navy font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-navy hover:text-cream transition-colors"
          >
            Meet the Team
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
